  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to develop an evaluative questionnaire, to evaluate patients with
      hip and groin disability, and a strength measurement for the hip, for patients with hip and
      groin disability.

      Both measurement instrument are aimed for evaluating the natural course and different
      treatment modalities in patients with hip and groin disability.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
